title: When Skins Just Suck - Rito Plz
body:
I recently got Beekeeper Singed, but it bugs on the dance animation.
He goes around once then stops.

The same happens on Dark Candy Fiddlesticks (that I have had since like 2012 or something).

I imagine this is something you can't or won't fix, as it's been around for sooo many years.
